rem cryotubes
rem 8/23/2017

do Examine Cryotubes
 [
  ifflag test cryotubes
   [
    print One of the valves on the cryotube ruptured when the system was tested.
    print Now dead scientist stand infront of the tubes, falling apart as you watch.
   |
    ifflag cycle system
     [
      print The tubes that line the walls are open, and scientists try to save these
      print strange hybrid creatures. Flushing the tubes have brought them out of
      print suspended animation and will probably kill them.
     |
      print The tubes line the walls in a semicircle around the room. Scientists monitor
      print the readouts, recording all sorts of information on company devices. Though
      print the mainframe must be doing the same thing.
     ]
   ]
 ]



